title: A Brand New High-End Luxury Apt in Uptown**Gas Stove!**
posting_body: ['A Brand New High-End Luxury Apartment in Uptown Dallas with Panoramic Views!!', 'Located in the Knox Henderson and Uptown Area it is within Walking Distance to Many Upscale Restaurants and Attractions.', 'Each Apartment Has Several Desirable Amenities, Such as Quartz Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Hardwood Floors, and Even a Built-In Wine Fridge!!', 'Other Amenities Included; Spa Bathroom with a Stand Up Shower and Oversized Soaking Tub, Walk-In Closet, with a Full-Size Washer and Dryer Included.', 'These Beautiful Apartment Amenities Include a Luxurious Resort Lounge Pool with a Tanning Deck, a Wellness Center, a State of an Art Gym, and even a Pet Park with a Pet Spa for Your Beloved Animals!', 'More Amenities Include a Golf and Sports Simulators, a Roof Top Lounge with Downtown Dallas Views, Plus So Much More!', 'These Luxury Apartments Even Include Climate Controlled Hallways, Parking Garage, Electric Vehicle Charging Stations, and Elevators, What More Could You Ask For?', 'Most Importantly They Have Great Management and Maintenance!!', 'Please Contact Jacquelyn with Dash Realty at', 'show contact info', 'For More Information About This Breath-Taking Property.', '**12 Month Lease or Longer, No Corporate Leases, and No Sublease**']
